headline: Tractor Supply price target lowered to $60 from $67 at Telsey Advisory
summary: Telsey Advisory lowered the firm’s price target on Tractor Supply (TSCO) to $60 from $67 and keeps an Outperform rating on the shares. The company continues to see further market share gains and strong customer engagement, the analyst tells investors. While the near-term environment may be more challenging and uncertain due to the tariffs, the firm remains confident in the company’s Life Out Here 2030 strategy.
